<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">No, indeed. His first book of stories, &quot;Plain Tales from the Hills&quot; was published in 1888. This book was published in 1902, and he had published quite<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">â€¦more</a></span><span class="fullContent">No, indeed. His first book of stories, "Plain Tales from the Hills" was published in 1888. This book was published in 1902, and he had published quite a lot in between.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
