        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer213736247" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18353703049846171969">OK, he&apos;s a racist blackguard, but Kipling does write beautifully. This was his first book I read in the original and I loved every bit of it - the stories and the pictures. Since I was too young to understand the latent racism (and there&apos;s so much of it in here, apparently) when I read it, and I have not reread it since, I will rate it based on my original reading experience - five golden stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText18353703049846171969" style="display:none">OK, he's a racist blackguard, but Kipling does write beautifully. This was his first book I read in the original and I loved every bit of it - the stories and the pictures. Since I was too young to understand the latent racism (and there's so much of it in here, apparently) when I read it, and I have not reread it since, I will rate it based on my original reading experience - five golden stars.</span>
