        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4873515" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16286712643369884495">Beautiful and wonderful. Works of genius by a man who freed himself enough that he could give himself up to that genius instead of trying to make sure that it came out perfectly. As pleasing as his other works are, none I&apos;ve read can match the joy, humor, simplicity, and odd truth of these. <br/><br/>Like children&apos;s literature should be, these stories never lose their humor or punch. Despite some redundancy with actual myths and some cases of artificially lowering complexity for children and hence growing</span>
  <span id="freeText16286712643369884495" style="display:none">Beautiful and wonderful. Works of genius by a man who freed himself enough that he could give himself up to that genius instead of trying to make sure that it came out perfectly. As pleasing as his other works are, none I've read can match the joy, humor, simplicity, and odd truth of these. <br /><br />Like children's literature should be, these stories never lose their humor or punch. Despite some redundancy with actual myths and some cases of artificially lowering complexity for children and hence growing transparent, eminently enjoyable.</span>
  <a data-text-id="16286712643369884495" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

