  <b>"So that's all right, Best Beloved. Do you see?"</b>
</i><br /><br />Um....not really.<br /><br />If you've ever wondered how the whale got his throat, (I'm not sure there any many people wondering about this), how the camel got his hump (perhaps, more likely), how the rhinocerous got his skin or how the leopard got his spots. Then, you might be amused by these unlikely explanations. <br /><br />My favourite is the one about the tortoise, hedgehog, and baby painted jaguar resulting in an armadillo. Intrigued?<br /><br />I'm not sure why this appealed to me when I was younger as most of it doesn't make much sense now.</span>
